Nigerian music star, 2Face Idibia who is a year older today has been getting messages from fans, friends and well-wishers but this message from his young son, Nino, stands out. Nino took to Instagram to share a photo of his father with the caption:   Through out my young life I have always looked up to you,every time I am in a situation I always ask myself ,”what will daddy do.”Then I remember your smile,the smile that brings joy,hope and peace to the Idibia family.I love you daddy and happy birthday A post shared by  Ninofabulous (@ninoidibia) on Sep 18, 2018 at 2:30am PDT 